
<section id="about">
  <span class="section-tag">Who we are</span>
  <h2 class="section-h2 serif">Small operation.<br />Institutional infrastructure.</h2>
  <div class="about-grid">
    <div class="about-text">
      <p>
        <strong>BBI Invest LLC</strong> is a South Florida ATM placement company
        founded on a simple premise: businesses shouldn't have to choose between
        good service and a reliable operator. Most ATM providers are too large
        to care about a single location. We built BBI Cash to be the opposite.
      </p>
      <p>
        We serve Miami-Dade and Broward counties — restaurants, hotels, bars,
        laundromats, barbershops, and condominium communities. We speak English,
        Spanish and Portuguese, because this is Miami and your clients deserve
        to be served in their language.
      </p>
      <p>
        Our processing and cash management runs through
        <strong>PAI Alliance — Brinks</strong>, a federally regulated network
        with 24/7 monitoring and full Regulation E compliance. The infrastructure
        is institutional. The service is personal. You get the best of both.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="about-cards">
      <div class="about-card">
        <div class="about-card-title">BBI Invest LLC — Active Florida Entity</div>
        <div class="about-card-text">Licensed and operating in the state of Florida. Available documentation and references upon request.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="about-card">
        <div class="about-card-title">PAI Alliance — Brinks Processing</div>
        <div class="about-card-text">All transactions processed through Payment Alliance International, federally regulated. The same network trusted by banks and national operators.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="about-card">
        <div class="about-card-title">$1,000,000 General Liability Insurance</div>
        <div class="about-card-text">Your location is named as Additional Insured on our policy. Certificate of Insurance provided before any installation begins.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="about-card">
        <div class="about-card-title">Se habla Español · Falamos Português</div>
        <div class="about-card-text">Our team is fully bilingual and we serve the Brazilian and Hispanic communities of Broward and Miami-Dade with the same level of care.</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
